px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>如果直播角色，则根据显示的性能，颜色开发可能会感到不舒服，闪烁和余生。但是，出现在舞台上的舞台上的两个巨头哈库金·乔加库因（Minato Hakukin Jogakuin）不仅有一个清晰的身材，而且根本没有不适或模糊。<strong>清楚地描绘了蓬松的头发和衣服下摆的颤抖，甚至牢固地捕捉了激烈的舞蹈表演的清晰度。</strong></p><p>顺便说一句，除某些人以外，该直播被允许拍照和录制，但是如果您写道：“即使使用智能手机相机，也可以清楚地捕捉到透明LED上的外观和动作。”传播一点？实际性能发布在“ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hashtag_click" target="_blank" rel="noopener">#double_xr</a> ”中，因此，如果您有兴趣，请查看。</p><h2>透明LED被扩展的“实时”表达，以及真实X虚拟混合体验的深度</h2><p>顺便说一句，如前所述，两个显示器之间的真实表演者有一个阶段。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 682px) 100vw, 682px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp 682w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-200x300.webp 200w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-768x1153.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-1023x1536.webp 1023w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp 1066w" width="682" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>换句话说，<strong>显示的数量为两个，但是该层具有三个层状结构</strong>。真正的艺术家可以通过在两个显示器之间站立，不仅是大型展示，而且可以在观众身上安装的透明LED来表演。换句话说，<strong>您可以将虚拟生产带到“真实”方面</strong>。透明LED的存在不仅对Vtuber，而且对真正的艺术家都是有益的。</p><p> - 我想在现场的上半部分，但是过了一会儿，我意识到还有另一层。在演出期间，通过透明的唱歌唱歌的大科<a href="https://twitter.com/Daok0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">（Daoko）</a>在展示之前就出来了。从客观的角度来看，只有“唱歌艺术家搬到舞台的前面”，但是那时，我觉得自己好像已经搬到了太空中，“我可以来到这边！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e